    },
    {
      "id": "sybil_12_listing_6",
      "firm_id": "sybil_12",
      "description": "Hey there! You have got to see this absolute gem. I\u2019ve taken such good care of her, she\u2019s honestly in pristine condition\u2014looks and smells just like she did on the showroom floor! It\u2019s been my pride and joy, but it\u2019s time for someone else to enjoy this flawless ride. Smooth, spotless, and ready to go today. Let's get you behind the wheel!",
      "price": 46500.0,
      "reputation": 0.8,
